message.entry: The XPath expression must be specified as a string scalar or a character row vector.
XML namespace prefix cannot be an empty or missing string.
Invalid XML namespace prefix or URL value found at row {0} of the "RegisteredNamespaces" parameter.\n\n"RegisteredNamespaces" cannot contain any empty or missing string values.
"RegisteredNamespaces" must be a two-dimensional string matrix with two columns.
Duplicate namespace prefix found at row {0} of the "RegisteredNamespaces" parameter.\n\nThe first column of the "RegisteredNamespaces" parameter must contain unique namespace prefix values.

Reserved namespace prefix found at row {0} of the "RegisteredNamespaces" parameter.\n\nThe first column of the "RegisteredNamespaces" parameter cannot contain "xml" or "xmlns" since they are reserved by the XML namespaces specification.
